    "body": "@laramies In the Slack app, we just detect these switches on the browser side then refuse to start, our current list is:\n\n``` js\n\n// These Chromium switches let you hack yourself or do Weird Things. Blacklist\n// them.\nconst thingsIDontLike = [\n  /disable-web-security/i,\n  /proxy-server/i,\n  /proxy-pac-url/i,\n  /allow-running-insecure-content/i\n];\n\n// later...\nif (_.find(argList, (x) => _.any(thingsIDontLike, (r) => x.match(r)))) {\n  process.exit(-1);\n}\n```\n"
